        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/elegant/scene_llama.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 26631f97-44f0-4d37-be99-425df5ff9144).Image",
        "Description": "Hello kiddies! Your pal the crypt keeper here. I love a good WHINE. Not a store wine, but locally GROAN. Everyone is just dying to taste the new MAULblanc. In fact, tonights tale is about a winery worker who found out a more than he should know. His employer doesn&apos;t like that, so he&apos;s hired an undercover assassin who decides to have a little fun on the job. I call tonights taste test &quot;Crushing Information.&quot;",
